Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:08.77,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}スピード増してく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:14.67,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}秋色の雲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:24.39,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}この頬に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:30.34,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}触れるその髪が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:36.76,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}とても愛しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:42.29,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}とても切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:49.15,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}離れたくなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:17:00.35,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}ねぇ　探してる　見つけたい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:06.12,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}形のない何かを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:12.09,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}人はカタチを見せるのが得意なの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:18.73,ED-JP,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\an7\bord1\blur5\fs54}遠い記憶青い母のように
