Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:31.43,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}拂过水面的忧郁微风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:39.67,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}试着轻声询问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:45.72,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}夏日已近尾声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:16:00.00,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}日渐西沉的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:08.77,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}也加快了脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:14.67,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}秋色的云彩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:24.39,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}轻抚脸颊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:30.34,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}是你的发丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:36.76,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}如此惹人怜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:42.29,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}如此令人伤怀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:49.15,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}我不愿与你分离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:17:00.35,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}我在追寻 渴望找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:06.12,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}那无形无影之物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:12.09,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}人们总擅长展现自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:18.73,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}记忆太过遥远 就像大海一般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:24.72,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}阳光下风平浪静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:34.36,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}似那浅眠的鸟儿 归去吧
